        <relatedmaterial id="ref9">
            <head>Related Archival Materials note</head>
            <p>The Lecture Notes Collection (AC #052) at the Seeley G. Mudd Library, Princeton University, includes notes on natural philosophy by John Maclean, Jr., 1857, and George Gray, which correspond to Wurts's. Gray's notes explicitly identify the lecturer as Stephen Alexander.</p>
